Note: No DB integration has been made and none (besides /health) of the routes currently work.
The Version 1 base url for the API: localhost:3000/api/v1/{route}. 

ADMIN: (base url: /api/v1)
    [/health] checks status of api. 

AUTH: (base url: /api/v1/auth)
    [/signup] creates a user in the user table with creds sent in request.
    [/login] logs the user in by checking their password against that saved in user table.

USER: (base url: /api/v1/user/:user)
    [/] middleware validates user exists by accessing an endpoint in the user group.

